00:56:17,030 --> 00:56:20,310
You should not use Me

741
00:56:20,510 --> 00:56:24,190
for your own purpose in that manner.

742
00:56:24,370 --> 00:56:27,710
But in any case you are using Me.

743
00:56:28,310 --> 00:56:31,810
But with the understanding that, "Mother is all the time with me

744
00:56:32,010 --> 00:56:35,290
and is helping me," there's no need

745
00:56:35,470 --> 00:56:38,990
to come forward and jump on My time and to take My time

746
00:56:39,190 --> 00:56:42,390
and to bother Me so that I should feel, "O God,

747
00:56:42,570 --> 00:56:46,470
